data.title: Ike Turner - Jack Rabbit Blues - 10" Vinyl + CD Album
data.meta_description: Ike Turner - Jack Rabbit Blues - CD
data.text:
Format: 10" Vinyl + CD

This package contains a 31 track CD, The Jack Rabbit Blues/The Singles 1958-1960, and a 10 inch Record, including the reproduction of super rare Tune Town 78 cut at 45RPM, plus a Retro Deluxe package & rare photos.

Every one of these tracks features Ike Turner on guitar, piano and/or vocals.

Also features Little Ann, as in Annie Mae Bullock, later well known under the famous name Tina Turner!
